    "body": "I think it would be a good idea to change the tests to be more complete : \r\n\r\n- [ ] Testing the client and the server against invalid packet ID.\r\n- [ ] Testing the client and the server against invalid data types (a string that's too big, an overflowing byte/int...\r\n\r\nIt may also be a good idea to use http://about.travis-ci.org/docs/user/languages/javascript-with-nodejs/ .\r\n ",
